These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, pink, ivory, white
4 different games are played: whist, go, poker, monopoly
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, martial-arts, action, sports
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, surfing, weightlifting, biathlon
 1. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing go##1
 2. the person who likes black is in an even position##4
 3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 4. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person who likes white##1
 5. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
 6. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person who likes ivory##1
 8. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's sport is skiing is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person playing monopoly##2
10. the person who likes black is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
11. the person playing poker is the person who likes white##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Color          | ivory  | black    | white    | pink   |
| Game   | go     | whist   | poker       | monopoly    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | mystery | sports    | action |
| Sport           | surfing | biathlon       | skiing | weightlifting     |

