.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, hot-chocolate, juice
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, police-officer, project-manager, lawyer
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, february, august, march
City: edinburgh, new-york, miami, rome
 1. the lawyer is in an even position##4
 2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
 3. the police-officer is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 4. the person drinking fanta is the person who's birthday is in september##1
 5. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
 7. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
11. the person who's birthday is in august is the project-manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage          | coffee  | fanta    | hot-chocolate     | juice       |
| Job         | project-manager | lawyer | dressmaker   | police-officer |
| Birthday   | august | september   | february   | march    |
| City         | miami | rome  | edinburgh | new-york   |

