.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
House: victorian, colonial, art-deco, cottage
4 different games are played: chess, go, billiard, poker
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, drawing, sudoku, cooking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, weightlifting, rowing, baseball
 1. the victorian house is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
 2. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person playing billiard##1
 3. the victorian house is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
 4. the person playing chess is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 5. the colonial house is the person playing poker##1
 6. the cottage house is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 8. the person playing poker is in an even position##4
 9. the art-deco house is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
10. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the art-deco house##1
11. the victorian house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| House      | victorian | art-deco   | cottage    | colonial      |
| Game           | billiard | chess | go | poker     |
| Hobby   | drawing      | cooking   | magic-tricks   | sudoku |
| Sport           | baseball         | ice-hockey       | rowing  | weightlifting       |

