.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, german, turkish, chinese
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, dannemann, ritmeester, cain
City: hannover, edinburgh, boston, berlin
House: gothic-revival, cottage, ranch-style, palace
 1. the polish is the davidoff-smoker##1
 2. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
 3. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
 4. the person traveling to edinburgh is in an even position##4
 5. the german is the palace house##1
 6. the ranch-style house is on the left of the polish##1
 7. the chinese is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
 8. the dannemann-smoker is on the left or right of the cain-smoker##3
 9. the ranch-style house is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
10. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
11. the turkish is the cain-smoker##1
12. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the davidoff-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Nationality   | chinese       | turkish   | polish   | german   |
| Cigar       | dannemann        | cain | davidoff    | ritmeester       |
| City      | berlin | edinburgh    | boston  | hannover |
| House      | cottage  | ranch-style  | gothic-revival | palace    |

