.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
4 different pets are kept: lizard, ferret, cat, snake
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, dahlia, begonia, rose
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite, coffee, hot-chocolate
4 different games are played: chess, poker, snooker, domino
 1. the person playing poker is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who growsbegonia is between the person playing chess and the owner of the snake##2
 3. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is the owner of the lizard##1
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 6. the person who growsballoon-flower is in an even position##4
 7. the owner of the ferret is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 8. the person who growsbegonia is the person drinking sprite##1
 9. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
10. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
11. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
12. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Pet    | cat    | snake      | lizard          | ferret    |
| Flower   | dahlia | rose       | begonia | balloon-flower |
| Beverage     | hot-chocolate     | coffee      | sprite     | almond-milk |
| Game   | poker   | domino | snooker        | chess   |

