.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, disaster, musical, comedy
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, skydiving, camping, photography
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, baccarat, ritmeester, swisher
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, tram, jet-ski, subway
 1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
 2. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3
 3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 4. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3
 5. the person watching drama movies is in an odd position##4
 6. the swisher-smoker is between the person driving the jet-ski and the baccarat-smoker##2
 7. the ritmeester-smoker is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 8. the person watching disaster movies is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 9. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
10. the person driving the scooter is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre      | musical  | disaster    | drama       | comedy       |
| Hobby          | photography    | camping | skydiving | cooking     |
| Cigar   | vegafina | ritmeester        | swisher    | baccarat   |
| Transport   | scooter  | jet-ski      | subway    | tram |

