 6. the cottage house is on the right of the person eating radish##1
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
 8. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
 9. the electrician is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3
10. the tower house is on the far right##1
11. the photographer is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
12. the person who's hobby is camping is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4      |
