The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, swimming, surfing, soccer
 1. the person who's sport is soccer is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person who's sport is surfing##2
 3. the fan of gospel is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 4. the person who growsbegonia is in an odd position##4
 5. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of techno##1
