 7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 8. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 9. the person who's sport is baseball is between the fan of gospel and the person who growssunflower##2
10. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
11. the person driving the taxi is in an even position##4
12. the person who growsorchid is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3

