The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, romance, horror, crime
 1. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
 2. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
 3. the person who growssunflower is between the person watching crime movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
 4. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
 5. the person watching crime movies is the person eating spinach##1
 6. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person eating lemon is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of r&b is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
 9. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
10. the person who growsazalea is in an even position##4
11. the fan of classical is the person eating banana##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |       3        |       4       |
