.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, light-blue, black, purple
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, november, may, february
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, zucchini, kale, asparagus
City: rome, boston, london, hamburg
 1. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
 2. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the person who likes light-blue##3
 3. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
 4. the person eating zucchini is in an even position##4
 5. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1
 8. the person eating kale is on the far right##1
 9. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
10. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
11. the person eating asparagus is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who likes turquise##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Color      | black       | light-blue | turquise        | purple        |
| Birthday         | february | may       | march | november |
| Food   | asparagus     | zucchini        | blueberry    | kale      |
| City         | boston     | london    | hamburg | rome   |

