.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
City: nizza, san-francisco, edinburgh, london
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, iris, dahlia, marigold
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, october, april, january
4 different pets are kept: horse, hedgehog, cat, chinchilla
 1. the person traveling to london is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person who growsorchid and the person who growsmarigold##2
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 6. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 7. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
 8. the person who growsmarigold is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
10. the person who growsorchid is in an even position##4
11. the person who growsorchid is on the far right##1
12. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| City   | san-francisco      | nizza | london     | edinburgh        |
| Flower   | dahlia | marigold  | iris     | orchid |
| Birthday         | october    | july | april      | january |
| Pet     | chinchilla | hedgehog     | cat | horse       |

 